snippet.title: Hazelnut Latte Official Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Hazelnut Latte is coming to Steam!

This visual novel transports you to Jade City where you meet a plethora of cute femboys and hot transgirls! Romance them and explore their stories in Hazelnut Latte!

Note: Sprites are outdated.
